article_title: Local medical provider recognized for outstanding quality and service
article_text:
Kokomo, IN (46901)

Today

Partly cloudy. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. High 81F. Winds SSW at 10 to 15 mph..

Tonight

Variably cloudy with scattered thunderstorms. Low near 65F. Winds S at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 60%.
